data.description: Gorgeous fully remodeled golf home with an incredible view!  Sit out in your back yard and watch the beautiful sunrise or hole #3 challenge golfers!  Open concept with so many unique features!  Brand new appliances   You won’t be disappointed!!  Chefs kitchen with plenty of storage!  Extra Large yard for a golf home. New hurricane windows. Equipped with 50 amp outlet for hot tub or swim spa.  Why buy “new prices” when you can have a fully renovated home on the golf course!  Serene master suite includes a Beautiful walk in closet with 2 chandeliers. Large walk in shower with a wall shower AND a rain head!  It doesn’t get much better than this!
data.whatILove: Excellent walking  neighborhood   Wonderful neighbors. Back patio faces East so you can enjoy afternoons and evenings without the hot sun beating down
